<p><em>Enacted by Presidential Decree, Wendell‚Äôs Diary Year 1</em></p>
<hr>
<h2><strong>Preamble</strong></h2>
<p>In recognition that every citizen holds unique gifts vital to the flourishing of the Republic,<br>
